            <h2 class="h2 mb-2 text-center">What makes Invisalign® different?</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="icon-wrp mb-2">
                        <svg class="icon" style="font-size: 1.25em;">
                            <use xlink:href="#key"></use>
